            <div type="a">
                <column>3</column>
                <head>The Slavery Question: Extract from the Speech of Peachy R. Graytan, Esq. of
                    Richmond, delivered in the General Assembly of the Presbyterian Church (New
                    School) at Cleveland, June 9, 1857</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Graytan spoke about the "Natural Rights of Man," using them to defend the
                    South's position on slavery.</summary>
            </div>
            <div type="l">
                <column>6</column>
